cs.GT, cs.EC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT) and microeconomics (cs.EC). The paper also involves the construction of algorithms (cs.DS) and the use of Bayesian inference (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses approximation guarantees (cs.LG) for the mechanisms proposed.
